    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/a84f76dec41cf8a1244e08089b5d0540.poster.avif?t=1763756598\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/a84f76dec41cf8a1244e08089b5d0540.webm?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/a84f76dec41cf8a1244e08089b5d0540.mp4?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Golf Game Where Speed Matters!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whack the ball and dash through chaotic courses, scored on shots taken and how fast you reach the flag. Every swing and every second counts in this fast-paced scramble — the lowest score wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Multiplayer Madness</strong><br>Tee off with 19 other players, swing fast, think quick, and outplay everyone to take the win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/bba3901bc02dc6bf780b370adb043ad1.poster.avif?t=1763756598\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/bba3901bc02dc6bf780b370adb043ad1.webm?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/bba3901bc02dc6bf780b370adb043ad1.mp4?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Types</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Royale:</strong> 3 holes, the slowest half of the field is eliminated each round. Only the fastest golfers survive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shootout:</strong> 18 holes, 19 players tee off, and the slowest player drops after each hole. Outlast them all to claim the win!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duos:</strong> Alternate shots with a partner to master courses together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tournaments:</strong> Post your score and compete for the top of the leaderboard.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Themed Courses</strong><br>Compete across a randomized mix of classic golf holes and tricky obstacle courses. Each course is a new challenge — no two rounds are ever the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/5d7863f39483f1dcdf6f315932cc87e4.poster.avif?t=1763756598\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/5d7863f39483f1dcdf6f315932cc87e4.webm?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294250/extras/5d7863f39483f1dcdf6f315932cc87e4.mp4?t=1763756598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization</strong><br>Putt your best foot forward with unlockable hats, skins, trails, balls, and clubs as you race to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb the Leaderboards</strong><br>Compete in tournaments and rack up points — be the quickest on the fairway and climb to the top of the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
